## 🏗️ ARQUITECTURA DEL MODELO OBJETIVO

```
Input: [B, N_views, 3, H, W] + view_idx [B, N] + attention_mask [B, N]
  │
  ▼
ViewConditionedBackbone (VECTORIZADO)
  ├── timm backbone: convnextv2_tiny (~28M params)
  ├── LoRA adapters: STACKED [4, rank, in_features] — torch.bmm
  ├── View embedding: nn.Embedding(4, feat_dim)
  └── Projection: Linear → LayerNorm → GELU → d_model=512
  │ [B, N, 512]
  ▼
AttentionFusion
  ├── MetadataEncoder: 4 embeddings → MLP → 64-dim
  ├── Metadata token → projection → d_model
  ├── Positional encoding
  ├── MultiheadAttention (4 heads, key_padding_mask)
  ├── FFN + LayerNorm
  └── Masked mean pooling
  │ [B, 576]
  ▼
ArcFaceHead
  ├── Normalize embeddings + weights
  ├── Angular margin (m=0.50, s=30.0)
  └── Logits [B, num_classes]
  │
  ▼
TemperatureScaler (calibración post-entrenamiento)
  └── Calibrated logits → softmax → top-3
```

**Total params**: ~30M (vs 89M anterior) — 3x más rápido, similar accuracy.

